# User Authentication Prompt for AI Development Tool

Overview:
Build a secure, scalable User Authentication system for LifeOps that supports email/password signups, social OAuth, SSO, JWT-based sessions, and RBAC. Include comprehensive frontend pages (Login/Signup, User Profile, Email Verification, Password Reset) and robust backend APIs with proper data models, security measures, auditing, rate limiting, and brute-force protections. All code must guard against null/undefined values before using array methods, initialize arrays with proper useState defaults, and follow the runtime safety rules explicitly outlined.

Project Metadata:
- PROJECT CONTEXT: LifeOps — Multi-Agent AI Operating System with audit trails, run artifacts, and a Cronjobs system. All auth events must be auditable, reversible, and permissioned.
- TARGET FEATURE: User Authentication
- Associated Pages: page_auth_login_002, page_auth_password_reset_003, page_auth_email_verify_004, page_profile_005
- Design System: Provided in detail (dark UI, specific color palette, typography, spacing, and component behavior)

# User Authentication

## Overview
Implement a secure, flexible authentication system that enables:
- Email/password signups and logins with strong password hashing (bcrypt/argon2).
- Social OAuth (OAuth 2.0 / OpenID Connect): Google, GitHub, Microsoft.
- Enterprise SSO (SAML/OIDC-based as applicable) with seamless user provisioning.
- JWT-based sessions with secure cookies or storage strategies (short-lived access tokens, refresh tokens with rotation).
- RBAC at resource/module level with audit logging for auth events and admin actions.
- Rate limiting, brute-force protection, and robust token lifecycle management.
- Clear onboarding flow and user onboarding wizard during signup.
- API endpoints and pages aligned with provided page names and semantics.

## Components to Build

- Frontend Components & Pages
  - UnifiedAuthEntry (LoginSignupShell)
    - Email/password sign-up and login forms with real-time validation.
    - Password strength meter integration.
    - Onboarding wizard steps (stepper: account type, preferences, onboarding tasks).
    - Social OAuth buttons for Google, GitHub, Microsoft.
    - Enterprise SSO (redirect to IdP) toggle with helpful guidance.
  - LoginPage (page_auth_login_002)
    - Email/password login form with “Forgot password” and “Remember me.”
    - Social OAuth buttons and Enterprise SSO access links.
    - Client-side rate-limiting feedback for failed attempts.
  - SignupPage (page_auth_login_002)
    - Email/password sign-up form with password strength indicator, terms acceptance, onboarding wizard integration.
    - Optional invitation code or domain restrictions for enterprise onboarding.
  - PasswordResetPage (page_auth_password_reset_003)
    - Request reset form (email), sending a time-limited reset token.
    - Token verification screen (with token from URL) and password reset with strength meter.
  - EmailVerificationPage (page_auth_email_verify_004)
    - Verification link handler, show success/failure UI with next steps and retry option.
  - UserProfilePage (page_profile_005)
    - Personal information management (name, email, contact), connected integrations, security (2FA enablement), API keys management, billing summary, and module preferences.
    - Session management (view active sessions and revoke).
  - RBACAdminUI (optional helper for admins)
