- API Endpoints & Methods (Routes)
  - Authentication
    - POST /auth/signup -> 200 with user, tokens
    - POST /auth/login -> 200 with tokens
    - POST /auth/logout -> 200
    - POST /auth/refresh -> 200 with new access token
    - GET /auth/me -> 200 with user profile
  - Password & Email
    - POST /auth/request-password-reset -> 200
    - POST /auth/verify-reset-token -> 200
    - POST /auth/reset-password -> 200
    - GET /auth/verify-email/:token -> 200/400
  - OAuth / SSO
    - GET /auth/oauth/:provider -> redirects to provider
    - GET /auth/oauth/:provider/callback -> process OAuth login
    - GET /auth/sso/initiate -> start enterprise SSO flow
    - GET /auth/sso/callback -> finish SSO
  - Profile & Settings
    - GET /profile -> 200
    - PUT /profile -> 200
    - POST /profile/api-keys -> 201
    - DELETE /profile/api-keys/:id -> 204
    - POST /profile/2fa/enable -> 200
    - POST /profile/2fa/disable -> 200
  - Billing & Integrations
    - GET /billing/summary -> 200
    - GET /integrations/connected -> 200
